A modularized online file editing framework, optimized for and including bitmap and vector-based image editors.


Requirements:

jQuery
Bootstrap (3+)
github.com/txje/ico-js
github.com/bgrins/spectrum/


Development roadmap:

Clean up and polish off simple pixel editing
Implement pour function
Implement color swap
Polish off localStorage saving/loading
  Better filename handling
  Warn before overwrite
Add ciphered saving/loading
Add simple test/code editing
Add git/Dropbox/HTTP/FTP saving/loading
Add spreadsheet editor
Add vector graphics editor (SVG)